tourCupDetails.title: FedExCup Fall Standings
tourCupDetails.detailCopy: FedExCup Fall consists of seven PGA TOUR events which will provide players an opportunity to lock up or improve their positions in priority ranking and secure additional playing opportunities for the 2024 FedExCup Season, which returns to a calendar-year schedule (January - August)
